item.title: Task 1: Reverse Engineering
item.description: Android Binaries L01.apk First, I went with the android binary L01.apk. I used an online decompiler called Decopiler.com to decompile the apk file. The decompiled files are available here. In the MainActivity.java file, I found that an alert box is made and its value is set to “This is the correct secret.” or “That’s not it. Try again.” by checking a.a(obj). We can see that a.a is a function in a.
